following the language "salary equity balance" in Section 23, Item 10.
SECTION 35 AUTHORIZATION FOR TRANSFERS – LANGUAGE
AND FURTHER AMEND by deleting the following new item at the end of Section 35:
Item __. Subject to the approval of the Commissioner of Finance and
Administration, a transfer of appropriations from Miscellaneous Appropriations to the
appropriate organizational units and programs of state government is authorized to
defray costs incurred by said units and programs for projects and programs previously
funded and obligated by allotments from the federal American Rescue Plan and
allocated by the state Financial Stimulus Accountability Group but incurred after
December 31, 2026. Provided, further, that no transfer shall occur until the following
conditions are met:
(a) All transfers shall occur after all appropriation savings are redirected
internally within the organizational unit or program to help defray said costs; and
