final cumulative fiscal note of the Fiscal Review Committee on such bill, if such bill
becomes a law. The Commissioner of Finance and Administration is authorized to
transfer such sum as described in this item from the Department of Education to the
Department of Correction. This appropriation is subject to such bill becoming a law, and
the fiscal impact of such bill being less than the amount indicated in the Budget
Document.
